name: Elite Warbird
description:
WORK IN PROGRESS

How to play:
Directional Arrows/WASD/Left Joystick to move

Space Bar/X button/A button to boost

Right Click/L2/Left Trigger to fire Triple Shot

Left Click (Hold)/R2 (Hold)/Right Trigger Hold to fire Standard Bullets

*Notes* Invincible while boosting but can't shoot
